{"tid":875490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叫雞權係男人權利既最後防線;雞蟲應受到保護","createTime":"2018-10-25T02:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T08:39:40.000Z","uid":117332,"like":27,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad34aaeddcb0b56905870bee5602e9e9f54c148","tid":875490,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"男人春袋俾人揸先搞到係女人面前成條狗咁，再唔係可以食住女轉頭既人都係男人最上層，佢地仲會一個人玩轉好多女。<br />\n而下面既男人只可以讓渡自己權利比女人，但好彩有得嫖先可以令部分男人係滿足需求同時實現自我，不過其他男人對女性卑微都會影響埋呢啲男人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界愈黎愈多地方禁嫖/娼，啲男人就愈慘。我地要捍衛地方既法律嫖權;就算叫得，都要同時唔譴責叫雞既人，因為佢地無錯之餘比好多男人仲高尚<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔叫雞，都要為左所有男人福祉保護雞蟲，人地罵雞蟲要幫人反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24efa07be659c8cde4bb2d5c1ed1e55f68176e07","tid":875490,"uid":90820,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"總結：樓主係雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5208aa809cc17cfab9b468dcc8ab012810180a86","tid":875490,"uid":117332,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"24efa07be659c8cde4bb2d5c1ed1e55f68176e07","tid":875490,"uid":90820,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:43:10.000Z","msg":"總結：樓主係雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:44:37.000Z","msg":"雖然雞蟲唔係咩貶義字 但我唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然一場平等戀愛同婚姻，對女方違背承諾都有錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38148d74cf0531f4adbe7165d355277257690752","tid":875490,"uid":117332,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"妓女係最誠實同偉大既人，更唔好講141既妓女係香港幾咁屈辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n初初可能俾人拐黎香港 比人呃黎香港 可能純貪錢 可能以為係輕鬆賺錢<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋計番工作風險高，又要成日俾警犬搞，又未必搵到正常工(可能比男人仲難)<br />\n<br />\n我覺得話啲女人係雞好侮辱啲雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為雞係女性之中不知幾高尚，堪比蘇聯衛國女兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047a902e4544ddaa7bcca5917c220733ee0a424f","tid":875490,"uid":195169,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死雞蟲<br />\n咁講條女做雞都應該受到保護"},{"pid":"a4d3e4f0bf8a7852c1a99620e6c7a50215c7d986","tid":875490,"uid":117332,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"047a902e4544ddaa7bcca5917c220733ee0a424f","tid":875490,"uid":195169,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死雞蟲<br />\n咁講條女做雞都應該受到保護"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"咁咪同有仔出去搵sp一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcdda161b39e3d02cdff24dabbfd93392733382","tid":875490,"uid":745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"如果做雞無錢賺 仲會唔會有人做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6237694067df997defe04a5529f37eaa079944","tid":875490,"uid":99048,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:04:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n<br />\n要俾錢啲女先同你扑嘢嘅全部都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31102d5fa790e9747ed0a00ee9914fa776e2765","tid":875490,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4d3e4f0bf8a7852c1a99620e6c7a50215c7d986","tid":875490,"uid":117332,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"047a902e4544ddaa7bcca5917c220733ee0a424f","tid":875490,"uid":195169,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"收皮啦死雞蟲<br />\n咁講條女做雞都應該受到保護"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"咁咪同有仔出去搵sp一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"你鐘意帶綠帽咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma